<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ900917-0114</DOCNO><DOCID>900917-0114.</DOCID><HL>   Hurco to Buy Back Common</HL><DATE>09/17/90</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A7C</SO><CO>   HURC</CO><IN>FACTORY EQUIPMENT (FAC)BUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK)</IN><LP>   INDIANAPOLIS -- Hurco Cos. said its board authorized thepurchase of as many as 650,000 shares of its common stockfrom time to time in the open market or in privatelynegotiated transactions.   The maker of computer-controlled machine-tool systems,which has 5.5 million common shares outstanding, said theshares will be held in its treasury.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>